115 (89%)</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891ce\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">2,893 (31%)</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891cf\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">1,538 (22%)</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-516891c6\"><p class=\"cl-51688153\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">Temperature</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891c7\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">55 ± 18</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891ce\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">57 ± 18</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891cf\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">56 ± 18</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-516891c6\"><p class=\"cl-51688153\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">Wind Speed</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891c7\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">11.2 ± 5.6</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891ce\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">11.7 ± 5.5</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891cf\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">10.1 ± 5.5</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-516891c6\"><p class=\"cl-51688153\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">Time in the Air</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891c7\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">152 ± 12</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891ce\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">147 ± 15</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891cf\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">146 ± 14</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\"overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><td class=\"cl-516891d0\"><p class=\"cl-51688153\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">Distance</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891d1\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">1,078 ± 42</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-516891d2\"><p class=\"cl-51688154\"><span class=\"cl-51671740\">1,032 ± 66</span></p></td><td class=\"cl-5168